   "stance": "supports",
   "quote": "Schneider Electric (France), Vertiv (US), Eaton (Ireland), Legrand (France), and ABB (Switzerland) are among the major players in the data center PDU market. Market participants are expanding their intelligent PDU portfolios and strengthening their market presence"
  },
  {
